{"word":"G2889 - κόσμος - kósmos - kos'-mos - Adorning","slug":"G2889","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κόσμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kósmos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kos'-mos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Adorning"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - kosmos</b> - <i>kos'-mos</i><p/>Probably from the base of <a href=\"#/G2865\">G2865</a>; orderly <i>arrangement</i>, that is, <i>decoration</i>; by implication the <i>world</i> (in a wide or narrow sense, including its inhabitants, literally or figuratively [morally]): - adorning, world."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2885\">G2885</a>, <a href=\"#/G2886\">G2886</a>, <a href=\"#/G2887\">G2887</a>"}]}